text: The 2014–15 Montana State Bobcats women's basketball team represented Montana State University during the 2014–15 NCAA Division I women's basketball season. The Bobcats, led by ninth year head coach Tricia Binford, played their home games at Worthington Arena and were members of the Big Sky Conference. They finished the season 15–15, 9–9 in Big Sky play to finish in a three-way tie for fifth place.
